# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# WeBuild — Environment Variables
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# The app works out of the box with NO env vars (demo mode).
# Add these to connect real services. See SETUP.md for details.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# AI Generation (enables real Claude-powered site generation)
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=""

# ─── Optional: Connect real services ──────────────────────────

# Database (PostgreSQL — enables cloud persistence)
# DATABASE_URL=""

# Authentication (enables OAuth sign-in)
# NEXTAUTH_URL=""
# NEXTAUTH_SECRET=""
# GITHUB_ID=""
# GITHUB_SECRET=""
# GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=""
# GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=""

# Payments (enables real Stripe checkout)
# STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=""
# STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=""
# STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=""
# STRIPE_PRO_PRICE_ID=""
# STRIPE_STUDIO_PRICE_ID=""
